text: Leptocyrtinus albosetosus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1943. It is known from Tonga.BioLib.cz - Leptocyrtinus albosetosus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Cyrtinini Category:Beetles described in 1943
